{"tid":1435623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[iOS]香城online 實時地圖推送文字廣播app","createTime":"2019-08-09T05:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T09:36:09.000Z","uid":33000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c8b56a6765538ae96c5269d71569403496090361","tid":1435623,"uid":33000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:57:46.000Z","msg":"傳送門: <a href=\"https://apple.co/2YWXq4c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple.co%2F2YWXq4c&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=048b7e14\" target=\"_blank\">https://apple.co/2YWXq4c</a><br />\n<br />\n之前睇左個Post, 係問IT狗可以為大家做d乜, 亦親身了解到當大家去到一個陌生既區域, 係好需要一幅好既地圖指引。<br />\n<br />\n呢個app本身只係一個工具, 需要各路市民既配合先可以發揮到佢最大既功效。 為大家提供一個即時既地圖資訊, 無論係警察封路, 交通阻塞, 示威者遊行或者係黑社會出沒等等...<br />\n幫助市民為突發既情況作出最有效既應對方法, 令大家<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">返工唔會遲</span></span>到或者其他...<br />\n<br />\n略盡綿力 希望可以幫到手<br />\n<br />\n暫時係測試階段, 未知Server既承受能力, 歡迎大家提供意見<br />\n<br />\n以下係隻App既簡單講解:<br />\n<br />\n呢隻App以開房間既形式運作, 暫定每個房間既存在時間為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">24小時</span></span>, 以防止太多舊資訊造成混淆<br />\n<br />\n建議使用方法:<br />\n - 預先透過其他通訊軟件組隊, 成立一個民間即時訊息通報小組<br />\n - 熟識各區既當地居民刻畫好當區有用既地圖訊息<br />\n<br />\n每個房間有兩個角色 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">管理員</span></span> 及  <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一般用戶</span></span><br />\n <br />\n<strong>房間資訊:</strong><br />\n - 分 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">公開</span></span> 及 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">私人</span></span> 兩種<br />\n - 顯示當前用戶數目<br />\n - 實時更新地圖資訊 不用刷新<br />\n - 顯示連線狀態<br />\n - 顯示最新廣播<br />\n - Like/Dislike 數目<br />\n<br />\n<strong>私人房間:</strong><br />\n - 全部都係管理員 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>公開房間: </strong><br />\n管理員功能:<br />\n - 新增/編輯路線<br />\n - 新增/編輯座標<br />\n - 發送廣播<br />\n - 顯示自身位置俾大家 <span style=\"color: red;\">（會以偵探圖案顯示在地圖上)</span><br />\n - 縮放至自身位置<br />\n - 縮放至最近更新地圖位置<br />\n - Like/Dislike 房間<br />\n<br />\n一般用戶: <br />\n - 縮放至自身位置<br />\n - 縮放至最近更新地圖位置<br />\n - Like/Dislike 房間<br />\n<br />\n* 房主可以透過會員編號增加管理員數目。<br />\n* 只要瀏灠過房間一次, 就會儲存係本地, 即使沒有網絡都可以係記錄到睇返<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k33x38D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk33x38D.png&h=cdd94947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oHCro8E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoHCro8E.png&h=202fba53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEjA110.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEjA110.png&h=d91023cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sngr8G1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsngr8G1.jpg&h=459165fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cry96tH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcry96tH.jpg&h=a7b4a0e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b079543cd0f3daabca7e84f74b7d27ab67127267","tid":1435623,"uid":33000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:50:07.000Z","msg":"註冊好簡單架咋<br />\n假email, 顯示名稱 加 密碼就可以<br />\n歡迎開新地圖測試"},{"pid":"34ffed230ab670d954ec95f312f489944fec5696","tid":1435623,"uid":33000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:54:51.000Z","msg":"推推推<br />\n呢隻app要多d人用先有效 單機就變左無意思"},{"pid":"dc55fb2399a268191a363412b81af07ced0192bb","tid":1435623,"uid":33000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:36:09.000Z","msg":"push push push 俾多d人睇到"}]}